programme.title: In Treatment

programme.desc: As Laila details an elaborate getaway plan, a sceptical Brooke learns that her patient's desire to escape dates back to her earliest memories - and has only been accelerated by societal injustice and the impossible expectations thrust upon her. بينما تفصل ليلى خطة هروب محكمة، تكتشف بروك المتشككة أن رغبة مريضتها في الهروب تعود إلى ذكرياتها الأولى - وقد تسارعت بسبب الظلم المجتمعي والتوقعات المستحيلة التي فرضت عليها.

programme.title: In Treatment

programme.title: Beecham House

programme.desc: With the arrival of his mother Henrietta and the discovery of his younger brother Daniel in a military camp close by, John has finally fulfilled his dream of having his family reunited.
